703816f-a.title: Brooklyn: Cortelyou Road - 40th Street
703816f-a.text:
(1)
Cortelyou Road, south side, west of East 4Oth Street, showing the
Michel Cummings house (foreground) which was occupied by W. Cummings
in 1873; and nos falling into decay. Also seen are rears of houses
which face East 39th Street.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(2)
The same area, further westward, showing also the Holy Cross Cemetery
at the right.
October 1928.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
